  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND CHAPTER 983, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 1996, AS AMENDED BY CHAPTER 957, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 1998, TO PROVIDE THAT THE GOVERNING AUTHORITIES OF THE CITY OF LAUREL, MISSISSIPPI, SHALL CEASE THE USE OF A CERTAIN PORTION OF THE PROCEEDS FROM THE RECREATION AND PUBLIC IMPROVEMENT PROMOTION TAX AND THE PROCEEDS OF CERTAIN BONDS FROM BEING UTILIZED TO FUND THE CONSTRUCTION AND EQUIPPING OF IMPROVEMENTS AT THE FAIRGROUND COMPLEX; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
